source: TEXT_BANKOB208_01342_SEQ_00<tab>Greed and envy go together like canker and mange, and Bo Gu has a mind to scratch both itches with a little help from his friends.
target: TEXT_BANKOB208_01342_SEQ_00<tab>Im Abbaugebiet des 789. Ordens plant Bo Gu eine Schatz<var 16 /var>suche.

source: TEXT_BANKOB208_01342_SEQ_01<tab>Zo Ga's trusted watchmen have hidden beguiling objects in the 13th Order workshop, and Bo Gu feels his quarters are much the better place for the mystery treasure. Let Ga Zi guide you to the workshop so that you may seize the contents of the fugleman's silverpots.
target: TEXT_BANKOB208_01342_SEQ_01<tab>Bo Gu hat erfahren, dass Zo Gas Handlanger irgendetwas Wertvolles im Alchemielabor des 13. Ordens versteckt haben. Schleich dich in das Labor und stiehl <var 32 ((EventItem)) 03F61E895B030502 /var> aus <var 32 ((EObj)) 03F61E9311030402 /var>! Wenn du am Eisensee den Alchemisten Ga Zi nett bittest, lässt er dich bestimmt durch den Geheimgang in das Alchemielabor.

source: TEXT_BANKOB208_01342_SEQ_02<tab>The silverpots prove to contain an enigma wrapped in a riddle. Whatever it is you found inside, you cannot dally, for surely the 13th Order is home to kobolds who do not share Ga Zi's inclination to bugger up the place. Deliver the contents of the silverpots to Bo Gu.
target: TEXT_BANKOB208_01342_SEQ_02<tab>Du hast <var 32 ((EventItem)) 03F61E895B030502 /var> in deinen Besitz gebracht. Übergib sie dem gierig wartenden Bo Gu im Abbaugebiet des 789. Ordens!

source: TEXT_BANKOB208_01342_SEQ_03<tab>Bo Gu receives the contents of the silverpots with much interest and very little comprehension. He is well pleased however, for envy is his great work and greed a mere diversion. If the stolen items bring him no profit, he is still a happy kobold for having deprived Zo Ga of what he values.
target: TEXT_BANKOB208_01342_SEQ_03<tab>Bo Gu hat keine Ahnung, wofür genau <var 32 ((EventItem)) 03F61E895B030502 /var> gedacht waren oder wie viel sie wert sind. Die Hauptsache für ihn scheint zu sein, dass du Zo Ga auf der Nase herumgetanzt bist.

source: TEXT_BANKOB208_01342_TODO_00<tab>Overcome any and all obstacles to acquire the contents of the 13th Order silverpots.
target: TEXT_BANKOB208_01342_TODO_00<tab>Im Alchemielabor des 13. Ordens <var 32 ((EventItem)) 03F61E895B030502 /var> aus <var 32 ((EObj)) 03F61E9311030402 /var> stehlen

source: TEXT_BANKOB208_01342_TODO_01<tab>Deliver the contents of the silverpots to Bo Gu.
TEXT_BANKOB208_01342_BOGU_000_000<tab>Shiny things they have in the 13th Order Dig, nice things they hide from the rest of us. Surely this is not right, no, no.
target: TEXT_BANKOB208_01342_BOGU_000_000<tab>Pst, <var 08 E905 ((Draußenlebende)) ((Draußenlebender)) /var>! Ganz geheimen Plan ich habe. Du mir zuhörst!

source: TEXT_BANKOB208_01342_BOGU_000_001<tab>There are watchmen in the 13th Order, Zo Ga's favorites, much loved by the fugleman, yes, yes. These watchmen have hidden pretty things in the workshop─alluring, inviting, pretty!
target: TEXT_BANKOB208_01342_BOGU_000_001<tab><var 2B ((<var 32 ((BNpcName)) 03F20A8E030202 /var>)) /var>, Handlanger von Zo Ga, im Alchemielabor Schätze versteckt haben! Keine Ahnung, was es ist, aber wertvoll es muss sein, ja, ja.

source: TEXT_BANKOB208_01342_BOGU_000_002<tab>Silverpots they are, absolutely oozing with worth and gorgeousness. And watchmen conceal them, how suspicious and ungenerous! The adventurer must seize their contents, and teach Zo Ga a lesson, yes, yes!
target: TEXT_BANKOB208_01342_BOGU_000_002<tab>Die Schätze stecken in glitzernden <var 32 ((EObj)) 06F61E9311030402 /var>. Du sie findest und öffnest und Schätze mir bringst, ja?

source: TEXT_BANKOB208_01342_BOGU_000_003<tab>13th Order Alchemist Ga Zi will guide you. Yes, yes, Ga Zi was the one who saw the silverpots.
target: TEXT_BANKOB208_01342_BOGU_000_003<tab>Wenn Ga Zi du nett bittest, er dich lässt bestimmt durch den Geheimgang ins Alchemielabor. Ja, ja! Los, los!

source: TEXT_BANKOB208_01342_BOGU_000_004<tab>Zo Ga and his watchmen have silverpots hidden in the 13th Order workshop, treasures they would conceal from Bo Gu and his deserving comrades! The adventurer will bring away the silverpots─spirit, whisk, bring them away!
target: TEXT_BANKOB208_01342_BOGU_000_004<tab>Die Schätze stecken in glitzernden <var 32 ((EObj)) 06F61E9311030402 /var> im Alchemielabor des 13. Ordens. Du sie findest und öffnest und Schätze mir bringst, ja?

source: TEXT_BANKOB208_01342_BOGU_000_010<tab>Adventurer, oh, adventurer! Did you find shiny things? Yes, are the precious silverpots' contents in our hands?
target: TEXT_BANKOB208_01342_BOGU_000_010<tab><var 08 E905 ((Draußenlebende)) ((Draußenlebender)) /var>! Deine Schatz<var 16 /var>suche erfolgreich war, ja? Zeig, zeig!

source: TEXT_BANKOB208_01342_BOGU_000_011<tab>Hem and haw, haw and hem. This is alchemical, yes, yes. But beyond that? Bo Gu is knowledgeable, but not an expert in alchemy, no, no.
target: TEXT_BANKOB208_01342_BOGU_000_011<tab>Hm, hm, alchemistische Zutaten das müssen sein. Hm, keine Ahnung, was man damit macht. Mit Alchemie ich habe nichts am Hut.

source: TEXT_BANKOB208_01342_BOGU_000_012<tab>What exactly this is, I do not know. What is it worth? Worth hiding─stashing, secreting, hiding! So, worth a lot, yes, yes.
target: TEXT_BANKOB208_01342_BOGU_000_012<tab>Aber bestiiimmt gaaanz viel wert sind. Sonst nicht versteckt worden wären.

source: TEXT_BANKOB208_01342_BOGU_000_013<tab>Nobody likes to miss such a thing─the loss of these mystery packets they will bemoan. Anything that vexes Zo Ga gladdens us─elates, heartens, gladdens!
target: TEXT_BANKOB208_01342_BOGU_000_013<tab>Bestimmt sie schon überall suchen, ja, ja. Auf Zo Gas Nase du herumgetanzt! Zo Ga immer zorniger wird! Bald wir ihn haben in der Tasche.

source: TEXT_BANKOB208_01342_POPMESSAGE_000_000<tab>You feel a watchful gaze─and murderous intent!
TEXT_BANKOB208_01342_BALLOON_000_020<tab>This area is forbidden to outsiders, yes, yes!

TEXT_BANKOB208_01342_GAJI_000_030<tab>Yunz got designs on the 13th's workshop? Bo Gu thinks there's a treasure in those silverpots I spotted─gems, exotic poisons, treasure, that sort of thing. Go and bugger up the place good now.
target: TEXT_BANKOB208_01342_GAJI_000_030<tab>Ins Alchemielabor des 13. Ordens du dich schleichen möchtest? Bitte, bitte, nur zu, hereinspaziert!
